| population  = 57527
| population note = &amp;nbsp;([[List of Irish counties by population|28th]])&lt;ref&gt;http://cain.ulst.ac.uk/ni/popul.htm Background Information on Northern Ireland Society – Population and Vital Statistics&lt;/ref&gt;
