==Hydrology==
{{seealso|List of rivers in Colombia}}

Colombia has four main drainage systems: the Pacific drain, the Caribbean drain, the Orinoco Basin and the Amazon Basin.

The [[Orinoco]] and [[Amazon River|Amazon]] Rivers mark limits with Colombia to [[Venezuela]] and [[Peru]] respectively.

