* Denmark has an embassy in Prague.&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|url=http://www.ambprag.um.dk/en/ |title=Danish embassy in Prague |publisher=Ambprag.um.dk |date=14 January 2008 |accessdate=14 April 2011}}&lt;/ref&gt;
* Both countries are full members of NATO and of the European Union.
