* The Czech Republic has an embassy in [[Baghdad]].&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|url=http://www.mzv.cz/baghdad/en/index.html |title=Czech embassy in Baghdad |publisher=Mzv.cz |date=29 July 2010 |accessdate=14 April 2011}}&lt;/ref&gt;
